    "body": "Some tests introduced in #11528 temporarily set the user's `config:build_stage`, which affected (or created) a config.yaml file in the user's `$HOME/.spack` directory that could leave entries behind if the tests fail.\r\n\r\nThis change ensures only temporary configuration files are used/affected by these tests.",
